<p><b><%= site.name %></b> is a bridge to <%= config.foreignName %> sites.</p>

<p>It lets you connect your pump.io account with your <%= config.foreignName %> account, and send your pump.io activities out through StatusNet.</p>

<p>It also lets you find your friends from <%= config.foreignName %> who are already on the pump.io network, and follow them there, too.</p>

<p>Registering on this service lets your friends find you, too.</p>

